@startuml
title Estructura lógica de datos del proyecto ATM

class CustomerEvent {
  event_id
  customer_id
  branch_id
  arrival_ts
  service_start_ts
  service_end_ts
  departure_ts
  observed_sex
  estimated_age_range
  transaction_type
  queue_entered
  abandoned
  served_flag
}

class ATMState {
  atm_state_event_id
  atm_id
  state_start_ts
  state_end_ts
  atm_state
  cash_available
  failure_flag
  maintenance_flag
}

class SystemSnapshot {
  snapshot_id
  snapshot_ts
  branch_id
  queue_length_total
  active_atm_count
  busy_atm_count
  idle_atm_count
  failed_atm_count
}

CustomerEvent --> ATMState : usa / impacta
SystemSnapshot ..> CustomerEvent : agrega eventos
SystemSnapshot ..> ATMState : agrega estados

@enduml
